                <head>255. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>Between August 5 and 9, representatives of the United States and the United
                    Kingdom met in Washington to continue their discussions on the problems of
                    transporting Middle East oil. For additional information, see the editorial
                    note, <ref target="frus1955-57v10#pg_734">volume X, page 734</ref>.</p>
            </div>
